games.description:
Start your career in a classic 4x4 SUV, with the subsequent expansion of the fleet after successfully completing missions on the road to victory!

Feature of the game:
- A lot of cool SUVs with real control physics;
- Increase your level of off road driving;
- Various cameras (including the internal camera from the cabin);
- At all locations a lot of springboards, pipes, obstacles;
- Realistic sound.

Features:
- modern 3d shooter;
- great racing;
- spacious open world;
- free content;
- fascinating passage;
- convenient and intuitive control;
- added additional options for customizing the image;
- the best weapons and equipment.

Welcome to the Car Crash Party  multiplayer arena!
This is the free edition of this new car-crash game with crazy rules
where you can challenge others players in furious matches online.

The LITE edition contains:

2 arenas;
12 differents crashable cars;
4 types of  power-up:
-pizzas &amp;  cakes make you heavier and stronger but also slower (choose your strategy) ;
-sand glasses give you extra time;
-dynamites trigger explosions 15 seconds after contact;
