Bandits Multiplayer PVP features online battles against other players. Control your bandit rider to win in a multitude of game modes.

Features:
3 horses; 
6 game modes: Deathmatch, Team deathmatch, Battle Royale, Zombie, Arcade, Pistol Deathmatch; 
Day/night toggle; 
3 Maps; 
Bow, Sword weapons, Pistol (only in Pistol Deathmatch and Zombie mode);
